36:02.227 --> 36:03.627
I really like his take on it.

36:03.629 --> 36:04.528
Right name?

36:04.530 --> 36:06.063
Yeah.

36:06.064 --> 36:07.597
So calling things
for what they are

36:07.599 --> 36:09.733
without adding your
