or apparently used to love,

01:10:29.926 --> 01:10:32.427
the father of your
illegitimate child

01:10:32.429 --> 01:10:34.495
can actually look after
her now financially.

01:10:36.433 --> 01:10:39.267
So you say maybe I can
just go play happy family.

01:10:40.637 --> 01:10:42.670
