01:12:06.656 --> 01:12:08.923
You love playing the
victim, don't you?

01:12:11.027 --> 01:12:12.760
Excuse me?

01:12:12.761 --> 01:12:14.494
Yes, it was you with
the broken heart.

01:12:14.497 --> 01:12:16.564
