01:12:26.543 --> 01:12:28.743
I was in love with you!

01:12:28.745 --> 01:12:29.777
You want the truth?

01:12:29.779 --> 01:12:30.845
What, is there more shit that

01:12:30.847 --> 01:12:32.347
